<h1>Why BCF NZ?</h1>	
	<p>About 25 men are diagnosed in New Zealand each year. Nine New Zealand women, on average, will hear the news today that they have breast cancer. 80% of people with breast cancer survive 10 years or more (92% if detected on a screening mammogram) but tragically, more than 600 women die of the disease every year. GIFTHUB NZ will donate 10% of our profits to the Breast Cancer Foundation NZ.</p><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>
	
	
	
